source: TEXT_SUBWIL035_00227_SEQ_00<tab>Fafafono has the look of a Lalafell dying to be asked if he has any work to offer.
target: TEXT_SUBWIL035_00227_SEQ_00<tab>Au Bazar argenté, Fafafono vous propose de gagner facilement un peu d'argent.

source: TEXT_SUBWIL035_00227_SEQ_01<tab>Fafafono has asked you to slay rusty coblyns and gather four bottles of coblyn grease.
target: TEXT_SUBWIL035_00227_SEQ_01<tab>Allez abattre des coblyns rouillés pour prélever l'équivalent de quatre pots d'huile chitineuse de coblyn.

source: TEXT_SUBWIL035_00227_SEQ_02<tab>You have collected the coblyn grease Fafafono requested. Deliver it to Adelard at the Hammers.
target: TEXT_SUBWIL035_00227_SEQ_02<tab>Vous avez réuni suf<var 16 /var>fi<var 16 /var>sam<var 16 /var>ment de pots d'huile chitineuse de coblyn. Allez les remettre à Adelard, près du Marteau du sud.

source: TEXT_SUBWIL035_00227_SEQ_03<tab>Adelard is happy to receive the coblyn grease, and is thankful to you and Fafafono for acquiring it. He explains that the hammers are creating a foundation on which estates for Ul'dahns of considerable means are to be built. Of course, not everybody is excited at this proposition, such as the Silver Bazaar's own Kikipu. It would seem that not everybody's idea of progress is the same.
target: TEXT_SUBWIL035_00227_SEQ_03<tab>Comme convenu, vous avez remis les pots d'huile chitineuse de coblyn à Adelard. Ce dernier vous a ensuite expliqué que les marteaux servent à consolider le sol pour permettre la con<var 16 /var>struc<var 16 /var>tion d'un quartier résidentiel à la place du Bazar argenté.

source: TEXT_SUBWIL035_00227_TODO_00<tab>Collect four bottles of coblyn grease from rusty coblyns.
target: TEXT_SUBWIL035_00227_TODO_00<tab>Obtenir de l'huile chitineuse de coblyn

source: TEXT_SUBWIL035_00227_TODO_01<tab>Deliver the coblyn grease to Adelard at the Hammers.
TEXT_SUBWIL035_00227_FAFAFONO_001<tab>Hey there, friend. I've a sure way into some easy gil, if you're interested. It won't even require you to break a sweat─well, not much of one.
target: TEXT_SUBWIL035_00227_FAFAFONO_001<tab>Hé, ça te dirait pas de te faire un peu d'oseille<var 1D /var>? Bah quoi, n'aie pas peur<var 1D /var>!

source: TEXT_SUBWIL035_00227_FAFAFONO_002<tab>All you need do is slay enough rusty coblyns to gather four bottles of coblyn grease, and then deliver them to a Hyur by the name of Adelard at the Hammers. Once he has the grease, he can use it to keep the hammers running. It couldn't be more simple!
target: TEXT_SUBWIL035_00227_FAFAFONO_002<tab>T'auras juste à prélever quatre pots d'huile chitineuse sur des coblyns rouillés et les apporter à Adelard, à côté du Marteau du sud. Un jeu d'enfant<var 1D /var>!

source: TEXT_SUBWIL035_00227_FAFAFONO_003<tab>I'm surrounded by fools here. They detest the hammers and the new way of life they symbolize. They care only for the successes of the past, but it blinds them to the opportunities of the present. Change isn't coming, friend─it's already here!
target: TEXT_SUBWIL035_00227_FAFAFONO_003<tab>Les gars du coin aiment pas les machines modernes de ce genre-là. Ils s'accrochent à la gloire du passé et refusent tout ce qui représente le progrès.

source: TEXT_SUBWIL035_00227_FAFAFONO_004<tab>I call the Silver Bazaar home for now, but I've no lingering affection for the place. I go wherever there is gil to be gotten!
target: TEXT_SUBWIL035_00227_FAFAFONO_004<tab>Moi aussi j'ai grandi au Bazar argenté, mais ces histoires me font ni chaud ni froid. Je travaille pour qui paye bien, point barre.

source: TEXT_SUBWIL035_00227_ADELARD_001<tab>What is it? Can't you see I'm busy cleaning the sand clogs from these hammers? Gods, I'd kill for a few bottles of coblyn grease right now...
target: TEXT_SUBWIL035_00227_ADELARD_001<tab>Qu'est-ce que tu veux<var 1D /var>? Tu vois bien que je suis occupé à retirer ce fichu sable de la machine<var 1D /var>! Ça irait plus vite si j'avais de l'huile chitineuse de coblyn, mais...

source: TEXT_SUBWIL035_00227_ADELARD_002<tab>Coblyn grease! Fafafono must have sent you. Thank the gods for both of you!
target: TEXT_SUBWIL035_00227_ADELARD_002<tab>Oh, c'est pour moi<var 1D /var>? Tu lis dans les pensées des gens, ou quoi<var 1D /var>!? Ah, c'est Fafafono qui t'a demandé de me l'apporter... Toujours là pour rendre service, celui-là<var 1D /var>!

source: TEXT_SUBWIL035_00227_ADELARD_003<tab>Before long, these tracts will be covered with the estates of Ul'dahn elite. But the ground is still too loose to build upon. The hammers are pounding to make a solid foundation. Once that's done, then you'll see the structures start to rise.
target: TEXT_SUBWIL035_00227_ADELARD_003<tab>À terme, cet endroit est destiné à devenir un quartier résidentiel respectable. Comme le sol est instable, on l'aménage grâce à ces machines.

source: TEXT_SUBWIL035_00227_ADELARD_004<tab>The building was planned to stretch even farther─to the heart of the Silver Bazaar, even. But it seems the powers that be are being met with some...local resistance.
target: TEXT_SUBWIL035_00227_ADELARD_004<tab>L'idéal serait de transformer une plus grande superficie, jusqu'au cœur du Bazar argenté... mais les habitants ne se laissent pas expulser facilement et ça ralentit nos projets.

source: TEXT_SUBWIL035_00227_ADELARD_005<tab>I hear some lass named Kikipu holds the rights to the bulk of the land there. Stubborn to a fault, that one. A bloody thorn in the side.
target: TEXT_SUBWIL035_00227_ADELARD_005<tab>Par exemple, il y a cette Lalafelle nommée Kikipu, soi-disant une ancienne starlette de la chanson... Elle est pro<var 16 /var>prié<var 16 /var>taire d'un grand terrain par ici, et elle refuse de négocier. Je n'ai jamais vu quelqu'un d'aussi têtu<var 1D /var>!
